resources.string: Look at the Image for the specified duration mentioned at the top of the screen.
After the specified duration, questions will be displayed to you.

This is Think fast, your recalling visual game.
This will help you with recalling visuals presented over a period of time. The aim is to solve the task provided by the game.

Remember you have to think fast!

This is Side quest, your daily diary partner.
This will help you with recalling events or actions presented over a period of time. The aim is to solve the task provided by the game.

Remember it is an adventure and you are the journey master!
